  <steps>
    <step>Read .claude/CHANGELOG.md to understand the entry format (date, files changed, summary).</step>
    <step>Add a new entry at the top (most-recent-first convention) dated today. Title: "Auth v2 in-progress markers applied (PF-1..PF-13)". Summary: "Renamed two fully-superseded auth pattern docs with DEPRECATED- prefix. Applied STOP banners to five partially-superseded pattern/constraint/architecture docs. Added prohibition section to project CLAUDE.md. Added pointer to audit doc in root CLAUDE.md §15. Will be retired when v2 ships (Workstream F)."</step>
    <step>List the files changed in this PR (the result of tasks 001-004 + this CHANGELOG entry itself).</step>
    <step>Commit with message: "docs(.claude): CHANGELOG entry for auth v2 pre-flight markers (PF-13)" + standard footer.</step>
  </steps>
  <acceptance-criteria>
    <criterion>.claude/CHANGELOG.md has the new entry.</criterion>
    <criterion>Entry format matches existing conventions.</criterion>
    <criterion>All files changed in PR are listed.</criterion>
